1016
01:29:09,333 --> 01:29:10,333
You are?

1017
01:29:10,416 --> 01:29:11,458
Xiao-Yun.

1018
01:29:12,583 --> 01:29:13,416
I'm A-Shan.

1019
01:29:21,500 --> 01:29:23,375
