1064
01:34:17,666 --> 01:34:18,583
My name is Jin Run-Fa.

1065
01:34:19,291 --> 01:34:20,416
Jin Run-Fa.

1066
01:34:21,208 --> 01:34:22,125
Nice to meet you.

1067
01:34:22,208 --> 01:34:23,208
I'm Tian-Yu.

1068
01:35:55,916 --> 01:35:58,458
Dearest Weiling,
